# ShieldGate API Gateway

ShieldGate is a configurable API gateway built with Node.js, Express, TypeScript, Redis, and PostgreSQL.  
It supports API key authentication and rate limiting using Redis and a sliding window algorithm.

## Features

- API key generation and secure storage (hashed)
- API key authentication middleware
- Database-driven rate limits (custom per API key)
- Redis-backed sliding window rate limiting
- Protected endpoints with flexible limits

## Tech Stack

- Node.js + TypeScript
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL via TypeORM
- Redis for rate limiting
- Lua for atomic sliding window

## Quick Start

### Requirements

- Node.js
- PostgreSQL
- Redis


### Setup

1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/saurabhdotdev/shieldgate-api-gateway.git
cd shieldgate-api-gateway
